{"tid":1446714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔係應該升級咩?","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:15.000Z","uid":103960,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9b73e629b11512f3877e572c6c3837895a238e25","tid":1446714,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"大家肯面對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">現實</span></span>未?<br />\n等政府跪底？少少誠意都無呀！<br />\n有人已經無咗隻眼！<br />\n班狗拉我地手法已經無所不用其極<br />\n亂鳩咁拉又得、混入黎拉又得<br />\n<br />\n大家仲要等到幾時？係唔係要等到所有前線比人拉曬先升級？<br />\n<br />\n居然有人仲話要勇武停一停？<br />\n咁咪姐係話俾對家聽，佢嘅策略係work？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家幾時先肯撕破係共產黨治下會有民主嘅幻夢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"d42a20cd341ddc86b9774c1af38a728d26ab87b9","tid":1446714,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"accbdfcc164028022abade56c19c4494c1cdef77","tid":1446714,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a501c8b032e0d4103d72997c56fea861297f8619","tid":1446714,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dd9822d04f346ea6a4b28a2b383180328a9c6de","tid":1446714,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"500895d68352d5d127f2e1818b9c70836ce4b944","tid":1446714,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"27b9f33af02408174500279512a9fe6c8f9c954c","tid":1446714,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3be743dda67559ed7122f91176e55c7db31b9d88","tid":1446714,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dadec0230d7cf339e87d718d88cb9ffb500685c","t